name: Omni Air International 767-328ER Rainy Landing Calgary
description:
Hey everyone, this is an Omni Air International Boeing 767-328ER landing at Calgary International Airport. Sorry for all the shakiness, it was really windy at the time. This plane was operating a charter for the RAF, so it was pretty cool to see! I hope you enjoy, and please comment rate and subscribe!
